Digital Gauge Demo
</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>
The Digital Gauge Control Demo sample demonstrates the entire functionality of the Essential WPF digital gauge. Digital gauge provides more powerful functionalities such as 7-segment display, 14-segment display, segment space, and width. Apart from this, complete customization is available using style and template properties of the Digital Gauge class.

</Paragraph>
